sequenceDiagram
    participant T1 as Task 1
    participant S as Scheduler
    participant T2 as Task 2

    T1->>S: delay(30)
    Note over S: Save T1 context<br/>Add to time queue
    S->>T2: Resume (swap context)
    Note over T2: Executes
    T2->>S: get() on empty queue
    Note over S: Save T2 context<br/>Block on queue
    S->>T1: Resume (time reached)
    Note over T1: Continues from delay()
